arcade literature the humanities and the world home join login blogs multimedia publications seminars rss about saturday march 17 2012 arcade home login alec hanley bemis view track alec hanley bemis's picture history blog view recent blog entries member for 2 years 50 weeks personal information biography alec hanley bemis lives in brooklyn ny but spends a lot of time in california he obtained his ba in history from yale university his writing has appeared in la weekly the new york times the new yorker spin asthmatickitty com the los angeles times and many other publications in 2001 he co founded brassland a record label that documents the work of a growing community of musicians including the national and nico muhly currently he continues to run brassland consults for the uk based music company all tomorrow's parties co manages the dirty projectors and acts as general manager at cantaloupe music in the past he has taught in new york university's graduate journalism program produced projects for the new media design firm funny garbage and written for faith popcorn's brainreserve website http ahb brassland org recent posts mxtape four beautiful songs for denniston hill 03 01 2012 6 42pm authenticity alter egos and bon iver a short attention span essay 02 15 2012 6 36pm mixtape three the mixtape mixed tape 01 23 2012 6 16pm the fireworks online & offline 01 03 2012 8 06am internet chanteuse lana del rey pros & cons 11 28 2011 8 11pm brassland is 10 a short attention span essay on publicity intimacy & the community behind the label's anniversary 09 30 2011 7 46am mixtape two funky 09 21 2011 11 06am september 12th 2001 to september 12 2011 09 12 2011 12 06pm mixtape one songs for the rapture 09 07 2011 2 26pm mixtape zero test pattern aka the changing nature of media consumption 08 07 2011 3 55pm real temples of culture a short attention span essay on el sistema mnmp art education & art institutions 07 19 2011 8 13am a short attention span essay on janet malcolm writin